  * [蘇阿姨的生日](http://maynyane.blogspot.com/2007/06/blog-post_18.html "http://maynyane.blogspot.com/2007/06/blog-post_18.html")，作者May Nyane 
  * [瑪西之聲](http://nayphonelatt.blogspot.com/2007/06/blog-post_19.html "http://nayphonelatt.blogspot.com/2007/06/blog-post_19.html")，作者Nay Phone Latt 
  * [詩一](http://thadar.blogspot.com/2007/06/blog-post_5373.html "http://thadar.blogspot.com/2007/06/blog-post_5373.html")／[詩二](http://thadar.blogspot.com/2007/06/blog-post_7699.html "http://thadar.blogspot.com/2007/06/blog-post_7699.html")，作者Thandar 
